    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like that. like a heavy fog. sometimes i look at the cliffs or the steep drops on these mountain roads and i wonder if it would be easier to just let go of the wheel and let the journey end here. like, if the road really does stop, why keep fighting to find a way back?",
